snippet.title: BARRICADE Development Update: Alpha 1.072
snippet.description: Barricade is a zombie horde shooter with a classic 90's aesthetic. Build barricades with nearby props to protect vending machines providing upgrades and ammo. Frantically juggle repairing, shooting, and upgrading your arsenal to survive endless waves of zombies that will test your barricade designs.
